-- Pettitte Tells Jury Clemens Told Him He Used Growth Hormones
-- B y   T o m   S c h o e n b e r g
-- 2012-05-01T18:29:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-01/pettitte-tells-jury-clemens-told-him-he-used-growth-hormones.html
Former All-Star pitcher  Andy Pettitte 
testified to a Washington jury that ex-New York Yankees pitcher
Roger Clemens told him he used human growth hormone to help
recover from injuries.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tom Schoenberg in Washington at 
 tschoenberg@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
